---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="PRODUCT CARE | ACHI Studio" description="Care guidelines to extend the lifespan of your minimalist clothing.">
  <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl tracking-widest uppercase text-brand-charcoal">PRODUCT CARE</h1>
      <p class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-gray-400 mt-2 font-light">Maintain the quality of your garments</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-sm font-light text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        ACHI garments are made from premium organic cotton, raw denim, and fine linen. Proper garment care preserves the fibers and ensures your clothes last for years.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-serif text-base uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-charcoal font-medium mt-8 mb-4">Linen Care</h3>
      <p>
        Wash linen in cold water on a gentle cycle. Hang or lay flat to dry to avoid shrinking. Linen gets softer with every wash!
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-serif text-base uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-charcoal font-medium mt-8 mb-4">Denim Care</h3>
      <p>
        Wash denim inside out in cold water to prevent fading. Avoid tumble drying; instead, line dry in shade. Wash raw denim as infrequently as possible.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
